  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dc5\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d96\u0dc2\u0db0 \u0dad\u0ddc\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A stock of drugs is found on Mannar beach",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy has taken into custody a stockpile of drugs that had been piled up on the beach of Ndukkuda, Mannar.",
        "During a patrol conducted by the naval ship Gajaba, belonging to the North Central Naval Command, in the Ndukkuda beach area, Mannar, a stock of drugs packed in polythene bags was piled up on the Ndukkuda beach, Mannar and thus taken into custody by the Navy.",
        "The market value of this stock of drugs taken over by the Navy is over 4.5 million rupees.",
        "It is believed that the smugglers tried to bring this stock of medicines to Sri Lanka illegally and put them into the sea due to naval operations."
      ],
